'''Shaper Adepts''' were members of the [[Shaper caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Adepts would be often continue to work with their [[Master Shaper|Masters]] after their [[escalation]], until they themselves were escalated to Master Shaper.

As they were escalated from Sharper Initiate to Sharper Adept, they were required to replace one, or both of their hands with [[Shaper hand]]s. However, Adepts Shaper Hands had five digits, instead of eight.

